graph TB
    subgraph "Kubeflow Notebook Controller"
        NotebookReconciler[Notebook Reconciler]
        CullingReconciler[Culling Reconciler]
        Manager[Manager Binary]
        Metrics[Metrics Collector<br/>:8080/TCP HTTP]
        Health[Health Probes<br/>:8081/TCP HTTP]

        Manager -->|runs| NotebookReconciler
        Manager -->|runs| CullingReconciler
        Manager -->|exposes| Metrics
        Manager -->|exposes| Health
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| NotebookReconciler

    NotebookReconciler -->|creates| StatefulSet[StatefulSet]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates| Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>80/TCP]
    NotebookReconciler -->|creates optional| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    StatefulSet -->|runs| NotebookPod[Notebook Pod<br/>Jupyter Server<br/>8888/TCP]
    Service -->|routes to| NotebookPod
    VirtualService -->|routes via| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway]
    IstioGateway -->|forwards to| Service

    CullingReconciler -->|queries activity| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|GET /api/kernels| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|GET /api/terminals| NotebookPod
    CullingReconciler -->|culls idle| NotebookCR

    NotebookReconciler -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    CullingReconciler -->|depends on| K8sAPI

    NotebookReconciler -.->|optional| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>VirtualService CRD]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| Metrics

    style NotebookReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style CullingReconciler fill:#4a90e2
    style Manager fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623
    style StatefulSet fill:#7ed321
    style Service fill:#7ed321
    style VirtualService fill:#7ed321
    style NotebookPod fill:#7ed321
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8
    style IstioGateway fill:#e8e8e8
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8
